---
title: Beyond Meat Taquitos with Plant-Based Mozzarella With Zesty Guacamole
description: Taquitos are a traditional Mexican street food that are typically deep fried. We’ve baked ours instead for a healthy twist! They crisp beautifully in the oven while the cheesy centre melts.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1032_W22_CA_RV159572-1_Main_low-58db0eb5.jpg
